---
title: Sausage & Warm Orzo Salad with Zucchini, Bell Pepper, and Tomatoes
description: Orzo is the perfect shape for pasta salads. In this dish, orzo is tossed with browned Italian sausage and a colorful medley of veggies for a gorgeous presentation. We’ve finished it with parsley and a squeeze of lemon to brighten the flavors.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/56966e7cf8b25e777b8b4567.jpg
